{"id":398,"ayahs":[{"number":15,"arabic":"فَأَنجَيْنَٰهُ وَأَصْحَٰبَ ٱلسَّفِينَةِ وَجَعَلْنَٰهَآ ءَايَةًۭ لِّلْعَٰلَمِينَ","translation":"but We saved him, together with all who were in the ark, which We then set up as a symbol [of Our grace] for all people [to remember].","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3355.mp3","surahId":29,"words":[{"id":17744,"position":1,"arabic":"فَأَنجَيْنَـٰهُ","translation":"অতঃপর আমরা রক্ষা করলাম তাকে","audioUrl":"wbw/029_015_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":17745,"position":2,"arabic":"وَأَصْحَـٰبَ","translation":"এবং সাথীদেরকে (অর্থাৎ আরোহীদেরকেও)","audioUrl":"wbw/029_015_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":17746,"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلسَّفِينَةِ","translation":"নৌকার","audioUrl":"wbw/029_015_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":17747,"position":4,"arabic":"وَجَعَلْنَـٰهَآ","translation":"এবং আমরা করেছি তা","audioUrl":"wbw/029_015_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":17748,"position":5,"arabic":"ءَايَةًۭ","translation":"একটি নিদর্শন","audioUrl":"wbw/029_015_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":17749,"position":6,"arabic":"لِّلْعَـٰلَمِينَ","translation":"জন্যে বিশ্ববাসীদের","audioUrl":"wbw/029_015_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":17750,"position":7,"arabic":"١٥","translation":"(১৫)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":16,"arabic":"وَإِبْرَٰهِيمَ إِذْ قَالَ لِقَوْمِهِ ٱعْبُدُوا۟ ٱللَّهَ وَٱتَّقُوهُ ۖ ذَٰلِكُمْ خَيْرٌۭ لَّكُمْ إِن كُنتُمْ تَعْلَمُونَ","translation":"And Abraham, [too, was inspired by Us] when he said unto his people: “Worship God, and be conscious of Him: this is the best for you, if you but knew it!","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3356.mp3","surahId":29,"words":[{"id":18750,"position":1,"arabic":"وَإِبْرَٰهِيمَ","translation":"এবং (স্মরণ করো) ইবরাহীমের (কথা)","audioUrl":"wbw/029_016_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":18751,"position":2,"arabic":"إِذْ","translation":"যখন","audioUrl":"wbw/029_016_002.mp3","charTypeName":"wo