 to provide sustenance for you: seek, then, all [your] sustenance from God, and worship Him [alone] and be grateful to Him: [for] unto Him you shall be brought back!","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3357.mp3","surahId":29,"words":[{"id":19843,"position":1,"arabic":"إِنَّمَا","translation":"কেবল","audioUrl":"wbw/029_017_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":19844,"position":2,"arabic":"تَعْبُدُونَ","translation":"তোমরা উপাসনা করছো","audioUrl":"wbw/029_017_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":19845,"position":3,"arabic":"مِن","translation":"মধ্য হতে","audioUrl":"wbw/029_017_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":19846,"position":4,"arabic":"دُونِ","translation":"ছাড়া","audioUrl":"wbw/029_017_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":19847,"position":5,"arabic":"ٱللَّهِ","translation":"আল্লাহ্‌","audioUrl":"wbw/029_017_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":19848,"position":6,"arabic":"أَوْثَـٰنًۭا","translation":"মূর্তিগুলোকে","audioUrl":"wbw/029_017_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":19849,"position":7,"arabic":"وَتَخْلُقُونَ","translation":"এবং তোমরা বানাচ্ছো","audioUrl":"wbw/029_017_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":19850,"position":8,"arabic":"إِفْكًا ۚ","translation":"মিথ্যা","audioUrl":"wbw/029_017_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":19852,"position":9,"arabic":"إِنَّ","translation":"নিশ্চয়ই","audioUrl":"wbw/029_017_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":19853,"position":10,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ","translation":"যাদেরকে","audioUrl":"wbw/029_017_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":19854,"position":11,"arabic":"تَعْبُدُونَ","translation":"তোমরা উপাসনা করছো","audioUrl":"wbw/029_017_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":19855,"position":12,"arabic":"مِن","translation":"মধ্য হতে","audioUrl":"wbw/029_017_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":19856,"position":13,"arabic":"دُونِ","translation":"ছাড়া","audioUrl":"wbw/029_017_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":19857,"position":14,"arabic":"ٱللَّهِ","translation":"আল্লাহ্‌","audioUrl":